            "value": "<p>A maestro's instrument can be crafted in the form of any variety of handheld musical instrument. A greater maestro's instrument grants you a +3 item bonus to Performance checks while playing music with the instrument.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You can play the instrument to produce the effects of an 8th level (DC 38) @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Charm]{Charm} spell.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You must supply a casting of <em>charm</em> of the appropriate level.</p>\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+3 item bonus to Performance checks while playing music with the instrument</li>\n</ul>"
